NOTE: The MIT license above covers the SOURCE CODE of this project only.

This is an unofficial, fan-made re-implementation of the board game
"Modern Art", designed by Reiner Knizia and published by Hans im Glück / CMON.
It is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by the designer or any
publisher. No official artwork, components, or trademarked assets are included.

Card artwork is NOT distributed with this repository — supply your own images
(see tools/gen_art.py / tools/import_art.py). Do not commit copyrighted images.
